peacekeeping missions in the future, South African Defense
Minister Mosiuoa Lekota said on Friday.
</P>
<P>
Introducing debate on his budget vote in the National Assembly
in Cape Town, Lekota said the defense function is about developing
and maintaining a capability to ward off threats or dangers
created by human beings or natural forces to South Africa and its
people. (SAfrica-Army-New Weapons)
</P>
