that we are ready to even discuss Kashmir, but a conducive
atmosphere has to be created by Pakistan for holding talks,"
Advani echoed Vajpayee as saying.
</P>
<P>
Vajpayee undertook the Lahore bus journey in an effort to
improve the situation, Advani said, adding that the armed
conflicts between the two countries last year in Kargil sector of
Kashmir changed the situation as the neighbor "augmented terrorist
activities" after the war. 
