from 133 member countries. Also present will be representatives
from non-member countries, as well as heads of U.N. institutions
and other international organizations.
</P>
<P>
The summit is expected to focus on globalization, the economy,
new technology, North-South dialogue and South-South cooperation
and solidarity. 
