<TEXT>
<P>
MEXICO CITY, April 6 (Xinhua) -- The Mexican state-owned oil
company Petroleos Mexicanos (PEMEX) exported 2.226 billion U.S.
dollars' worth of crude oil during the first two months of this
year, up 1.201 billion dollars over the same period of last year.
</P>
