18 formations of U.S. and British warplanes made 48 armed sorties
from Saudi Arabia and Kuwait, flying over the southern provinces
of Basra, Thi-Qar, Misan, Muthana Qadissiyah, Wasit and Najaf,
announced an Iraqi military spokesman. (Iraq-U.S.)
</P>
